      "evidence_quote": "\"It was just a screen name, not a lie.\"",
      "rationale": "Limited evidence of inquiry/research skills: the piece uses a small amount of textual evidence but does not demonstrate research, question-driven investigation, or required citation practices (e.g., author/page in MLA) expected in the assignment outline."
    },
    {
      "criterion_id": "C1",
      "level": "4",
